{"tid":188684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"2017人生新開始，無論正評負評都祝福你","createTime":"2017-04-06T00:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T04:12:42.000Z","uid":19126,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"037065d0c38ada95a301e6f79e68f7e96efb7058","tid":188684,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T00:42:33.000Z","msg":"2016年年尾，40日內同阿媽反面、情緒問題因為小事得罪朋友反埋面、出街遇騙子雖然搞左半個月之後冇事，最後發現埋帽事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生好似瞬間崩潰，到依家，都仲係好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過今日係我生日，想係度許個願，希望認真拍拖既人都搵到認真既另一半 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  受到情傷既你會得到上天眷顧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想祝自己心想事成，所有野都順順利利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfe08a4cea5457e45933598f61baf60e6ebf6f9","tid":188684,"uid":3113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T00:47:33.000Z","msg":"happy birthday <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f2f9e181bc88ca619fe29d575baac8c7ac4e58","tid":188684,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T00:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>happy birthday <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ce5451098d738a366beda74141200f53b69cd5","tid":188684,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T00:50:28.000Z","msg":"小事啦 ！<br />\n眨下眼就過"},{"pid":"95da6c756c2dd343b71fb59ddad56644fafe7481","tid":188684,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T00:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小事啦 ！<br />\n眨下眼就過</blockquote><br />\n都係既，不經不覺就四月啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <